      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Studdinajeet eekſch Juh-\nda un Jeruſalemēs/ leezeet to\ndſirdeht un ſtahſtaſt; Baſunet\nar Baſuni tai Semmē/ fanzeet\nar piſnu (Mutti) un faſkaſt:\nGapulzinajtees/ un laiſchat\nmunis ee-eet ſtiprōs Pilſfahtōs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Iſzelleet weenu Karrogu\neekſch Zianas/ ſtiprinajeetees/ ne\nſtahweet. Jo es atweddu Lau-\nnunu no Geemeka-Pufes/ un\nweenu leeſu Satreeſchann.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Taß Lauwa uſkahpj no ta-\nwas Allag/ un tas Lauschu Mat-\ntatajs irr uhs angſchu zehſees/\nwiſch irr iegahjts no tawas\nWeetas tawu Semuni pohſtā\ndarriht/ tawi Pilſfahti taps iſ-\npohſtiti/ ka neweens tur wairs\nDiſhwohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Tadeht apjohſeet Maiſus/\nschehlojeetees un kauzeet/ jo tas\nKarſtums tahs Bahrsibas ta\nKUNGĀ ne irr no mums no-\nwehrſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Tai Deenā/ faſka tas\nKUNGŚ/ iſnihēs ta Sirds\nDrohſchiba ta Kehnina/ un ta\nSirds Drohſchiba to Leeſu-Kun-\ngu/ un tee Preesteri iſbihſees/\nun tee Praueefchi iſtruhzinajſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "10. Tad fazzijn es: Ak\nKlings/ KUNGŚ! Pateſti/ tu\neſti ſchohs Landis un Jeruſalemē\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Tanni Laikā taps uhe-\nscheem Landim/ un uhs Jeruſa-\nlemi faazzihts: Weens ſaute-\nWehſch nahk no tahm augſtahm\nWeetahn/ Tuſſneti us to Zelt-\ntahs Meitas mannu Lauschu\nne Wehtifchanas/ ne Schihſti-\nſchanas pehz.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Weens Wehſch ma-\nnahks/ kas ſtipraks buhs nek-\nwinni/ tad ir es to Teetu pret-\nwinneem nefflichu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Raugi/ wiſch uſkahp-\ntā Padebbefis/ un winna Ratt-\nirr ka weens Weefulis/ win-\nSirgi irr tſchaklaki nekā Ebrgti-\nwaj mumis! jo mehs effin-\npohſtiti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Masga tawu Sirđi n-\nLaunuma/ Jeruſalemē/ ka tu-\ntehti iegkahbta/ zik ilgi liſſi t-\ntahs Dohmas tawas Neleetiba-\ntawas Sirđs Widdū palikt?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Jo weena Balkſne flud-\ndina no Danna/ un ieteiz Be-\ndas no teem Kalneem Eewraim-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Darrajt teem Paganeen-\nsinnamu/ raugi/ iſteizeet pret-\nJeruſalemē: Sargi nahk no tah-\ntas Semmes/ un tee pazelf fa-\nwu Balkni prett teem Pilſfah-\nteem Juha.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Ka tee Sargi Tſhruinā-\ntā buhs tee apkahrt prett win-\nnu/ tadeht ka ta irr pahrgalwig-\npret\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
